Class FileCreator.FileConfiguration.FileRunConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.donkeycore.dpl.io.FileCreator.FileConfiguration.FileRunConfiguration
  • Enclosing class:
    FileCreator.FileConfiguration

    public final class FileCreator.FileConfiguration.FileRunConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    A configuration instance used after a file runs. FileCreator.FileConfiguration is used to edit code before the file runs.
    Since:
    1.0
